      <title>加密货币巨头的 1.6 亿美元战争资金威胁参议院民主党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/crypto-titans-160-million-war-chest-threatens-senate-democrats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币亿万富翁及其盟友已经积累了 1.6 亿美元的资金，通过支持支持对陷入困境的行业进行轻度监管的美国候选人来保护他们的财富。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/crypto-titans-160-million-war-chest-threatens-senate-democrats</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
